&lt;li&gt;Draft and negotiate agreements for software, SAAS, advertising, production, talent, content, marketing and other commercial transactions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Counsel our teams on many legal and business issues, including rights and clearances.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with diverse partners, including esports, procurement, business development, partnerships, marketing, sales, and finance.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with legal team members to improve processes and ensure business demands are satisfied.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
