&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s Degree or equivalent;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3 to 6 years of experience navigating commercial transactions, preferably in the digital space&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience drafting and closing commercial agreements and improving contracting processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work independently while also contributing successfully to cross-functional teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sound judgment even in ambiguous situations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong communication and analytical skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bonus Points&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior experience on a legal team at a media, internet, or technology company&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of Twitch, including esports / gaming, UGC services, and digital media business trends&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Perks&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Medical, Dental, Vision &amp;amp

