&lt;li&gt;Own the intake, planning, coordination, and tracking of legal compliance initiatives from initial request through completion.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the primary architect of AI-powered solutions and be responsible for driving effective adoption of AI-enabled legal solutions within the legal team.&lt;/li&gt;
